{"tid":2436523,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日令午(偏遠地區)","createTime":"2021-03-07T07:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T13:23:11.000Z","uid":176449,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"402264f40e32ddba02e7273ee0c54b466af245d9","tid":2436523,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"今日入咗偏遠地區食嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xHfe7ZA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxHfe7ZA.png&h=7813303b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗌咗炸雞餐同炸豬扒餐<br />\n套餐包味噌湯 茶碗蒸 仲有玄米茶<br />\n女朋友嗌咗個富士山特飲<br />\n我嗌咗個飲落同芬達冇分別嘅日本汽水<br />\n仲加咗個芝士玉子燒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mncMY7r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmncMY7r.png&h=4425e93e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗌完一陣就上咗芝士玉子燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正正常常冇乜特別<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3O1qvgq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3O1qvgq.png&h=76e6e6d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n茶碗蒸實咗少少 上次嚟食滑啲<br />\n但係好食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入面有冬菇同魚板<br />\n味噌湯就係味噌湯嘅味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4GRqQw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4GRqQw.png&h=e8869eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炸豬扒厚身唔會乾 又大份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果你哋食可以叫老細落多少少醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n富士山飲落係海鹽奶蓋加梳打嘅味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ZwmN5q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZwmN5q.png&h=51cbc6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbufSxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbufSxv.jpg&h=214dfe47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好大舊雞 有肉汁！但唔夠味 <br />\n如果有他他醬跟埋就更送飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LPrZdP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LPrZdP.png&h=5967b585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n痴撚線仲送埋奶凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾滑同好重cream味 但可以甜少少少少少<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHsASzM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHsASzM.png&h=84ab6a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過女朋友依杯就炒咗車<br />\n應該放過入冰箱 搞到入面好鞋同結冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後仲有玄米茶飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飽到仆街<br />\n<br />\n其實之前食過一次<br />\n我覺得佢嘅豚丼同烏冬好食啲<br />\n今次嗌嘅依兩個都冇汁 冇得送飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出咁詳細嘅post係因為<br />\n見佢哋平日午巿好似都唔多人<br />\n同得兩個老細(?)一腳踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見佢哋請緊人 <br />\n住附近失業就去望下啱唔啱自己做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋咁多嘢食加埋價錢幾抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989bf5891882535bb45c6a8826a20e43d6909d48","tid":2436523,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"屯門？"},{"pid":"f1d33030d47e771265d7ae12ed12fa7e48133258","tid":2436523,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989bf5891882535bb45c6a8826a20e43d6909d48","tid":2436523,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"屯門？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:29:11.000Z","msg":"死 唔記得講邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺顯徑 間嘢叫創"},{"pid":"ced5f3fb8c60d830da4673f7a6c2263502d4be32","tid":2436523,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:30:20.000Z","msg":"好似係新開嘅<br />\n喺黃藍地圖未見到有<br />\n但前排見佢有痴文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5c895f34cfa4b84265ce00d2de39493e3aea4e","tid":2436523,"uid":392196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"睇相都知唔好食"},{"pid":"237d74a71e471c9787718c27422c4a1ed1137f8d","tid":2436523,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5c895f34cfa4b84265ce00d2de39493e3aea4e","tid":2436523,"uid":392196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"睇相都知唔好食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"Ok啦 依兩個正正常常<br />\n豚肉丼會好食啲囉<br />\n但係我覺得佢重點係扺食<br />\n一個set包好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ada5f3d45dc39b51356e1cb827d2840712e3f8","tid":2436523,"uid":392196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237d74a71e471c9787718c27422c4a1ed1137f8d","tid":2436523,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5c895f34cfa4b84265ce00d2de39493e3aea4e","tid":2436523,"uid":392196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"睇相都知唔好食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"Ok啦 依兩個正正常常<br />\n豚肉丼會好食啲囉<br />\n但係我覺得佢重點係扺食<br />\n一個set包好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T10:40:33.000Z","msg":"成舊水"},{"pid":"11385bd8e537f054cd703f2861d543dfb4e9ffdf","tid":2436523,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ada5f3d45dc39b51356e1cb827d2840712e3f8","tid":2436523,"uid":392196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237d74a71e471c9787718c27422c4a1ed1137f8d","tid":2436523,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5c895f34cfa4b84265ce00d2de39493e3aea4e","tid":2436523,"uid":392196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"